  "method_notes": {
    "share_weights": "IEA market and scenario evidence is translated into GCAM share-weights, not copied one-for-one as sales shares. Ordering is preserved across SSPs and the schedules are calibrated so BEV adoption is fastest in SSP1, central in SSP2, slowest in SSP3 and SSP4, and technology-led but not climate-constrained in SSP5.",
